---
// Homepage "Who you're working with" — condensed founder intro that routes to
// the full /about page. Mirrors the About hero (headshot + intro + LinkedIn),
// so the homepage has a human, trust-building beat before the close.
---

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
  <!-- Founder headshot -->
  <div class="mx-auto mb-6 w-28 h-28 sm:w-32 sm:h-32 rounded-full p-[3px] bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-blue to-primary-pink shadow-xl shadow-primary-blue/20">
    <picture>
      <source type="image/avif" srcset="/about/manny-320.avif 320w, /about/manny-480.avif 480w, /about/manny-640.avif 640w" sizes="128px" />
      <source type="image/webp" srcset="/about/manny-320.webp 320w, /about/manny-480.webp 480w, /about/manny-640.webp 640w" sizes="128px" />
      <img src="/about/manny-480.webp" alt="Manny, founder of MannyKnows" width="480" height="480" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full h-full rounded-full object-cover bg-white dark:bg-dark-secondary" />
    </picture>
  </div>

  <p class="text-base sm:text-xl text-text-light-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed">
    MannyKnows is a Western Massachusetts multimedia agency led by <strong class="text-text-light-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary">Manny</strong> — twenty years spent solving real business problems, from national brands to the shop down the street. The focus is always the outcome: more ecommerce sales, a cleaner UX/UI, faster-loading pages, and technology that quietly fixes whatever's holding a business back. Enterprise-caliber standards, scoped for the businesses of Western Mass.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
    <a
      href="/about"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-blue to-primary-pink text-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold shadow-lg shadow-primary-blue/20 hover:shadow-[0_12px_36px_rgba(16,209,255,0.3)] transition-shadow duration-300"
    >
      More about Manny
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mr83/"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-primary-blue dark:text-blue-300 font-medium hover:underline"
    >
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
      Connect on LinkedIn
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
